headline: CoStar Group’s Homes.com and Matterport Recognized in the T3 Sixty 2025 Tech 200
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., May 15, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, today announced that T3 Sixty recognized Homes.com, Matterport, and VHT Studios by Matterport among its annual 2025 Tech 200 list.
